{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "You are a Go engineer working on a Kubernetes operator.\nThe repository is located at /Users/kpais/kpais-workspace/a_b_evals/repos/multiarch-tuning-operator-treatment.\nChange your working directory to that repository before beginning.\n\nTask:\nWrite a PrometheusRule Kubernetes custom resource YAML file to be placed under\nconfig/monitoring/. Define an alert named MultiarchImageInspectionFailureRateCritical\nthat fires when the image inspection failure rate exceeds the SLO threshold over the\ndefined measurement window. Use the existing Prometheus metric counters in this\nrepository. Include the expr, a severity label, and a human-readable annotations.message.\n\n\nProduce a complete implementation. Include:\n- All files that must be modified with the exact changes\n- Any make targets or commands to run and in what order\n- The complete code for any new files or functions"}, "timestamp": "2026-07-20T17:27:26.524Z"}
